cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses deep multitask learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments involve computer vision tasks (cs.CV) and natural language processing tasks (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and the development of a soft ordering approach, which involves learning how shared layers are applied in different ways for different tasks, indicating a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
